  The following would clip the first 30 seconds, and then clip everything that is 10 seconds after that:
  https://trac.ffmpeg.org/wiki/Seeking
  ffmpeg -ss 00:01:00 -i video.mp4 -to 00:02:00 -c copy -copyts cut.mp4
